queries.query: SELECT      c.c_custkey,      COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS order_count,      SUM(EXP(EXP(o.o_totalprice))) AS exp_totalprice_sum FROM      tpch9g.customer c JOIN      tpch9g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey GROUP BY      c.c_custkey;
SELECT EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))))), LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity)))))), SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity)))))) FROM tpch500m.lineitem l WHERE l.l_quantity > 50;

SELECT l_returnflag,         l_linestatus,         SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,         SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,         AVG(l_discount) AS avg_discount FROM tpch9g.lineitem WHERE l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' GROUP BY l_returnflag, l_linestatus ORDER BY l_returnflag, l_linestatus;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM tpch5g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50 ORDER BY l_extendedprice DESC, l_discount ASC;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_quantity,      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))) AS exp_val,      LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))) AS log_val,      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) AS sin_val,      COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(l_quantity)))))) AS cos_val FROM tpch1g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_quantity, SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) FROM tpch9g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50 ORDER BY l_orderkey DESC;

SELECT     c.c_nationkey,     COUNT(*) AS num_orders,     SUM(EXP(EXP(EXP(o.o_totalprice)))) AS complex_agg FROM     tpch1g.customer c JOIN     tpch1g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey GROUP BY     c.c_nationkey;

SELECT      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus,      SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,      SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS sum_disc_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS sum_charge,      AVG(l_quantity) AS avg_qty,      AVG(l_extendedprice) AS avg_price,      AVG(l_discount) AS avg_disc,      COUNT(*) AS count_order FROM      tpch5g.lineitem GROUP BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus ORDER BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice, l_discount FROM tpch500m.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50 ORDER BY l_extendedprice DESC, l_discount ASC;

SELECT      c.c_custkey,      COUNT(o.o_orderkey) AS order_count,      SUM(EXP(EXP(EXP(o.o_totalprice)))) AS exp_totalprice_sum FROM      tpch5g.customer c JOIN      tpch5g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey GROUP BY      c.c_custkey;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_quantity,      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))) AS exp_calc,      LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))) AS log_calc,      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) AS sin_calc,      COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(l_quantity)))))) AS cos_calc FROM tpch5g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;

SELECT      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))))),     LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity)))))),     SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity)))))),     o.o_orderkey,     o.o_orderdate FROM      tpch1g.lineitem l JOIN      tpch1g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey;

SELECT      c.c_name,      o.o_orderdate,      l.l_extendedprice,      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity)))))) AS complex_calculation FROM      tpch9g.customer c JOIN      tpch9g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN      tpch9g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE      o.o_orderdate >= '1995-01-01' ORDER BY      l.l_extendedprice DESC;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_extendedprice, l_discount, SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity))) AS complex_calculation FROM tpch1g.lineitem WHERE l_shipdate > '1995-01-01' ORDER BY complex_calculation DESC, l_orderkey;
SELECT l_quantity, EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))), LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))), SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) FROM tpch500m.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;

SELECT     n.n_name,     COUNT(*) AS num_orders,     SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS total_revenue FROM     tpch1g.orders o JOIN     tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN     tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN     tpch1g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE     l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY     n.n_name;
SELECT EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))), LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))), SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) FROM tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT      o.o_orderkey,      l.l_partkey,      l.l_quantity,      c.c_custkey,      c.c_name,      s.s_suppkey,      s.s_name FROM      tpch9g.orders o JOIN      tpch9g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN      tpch9g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN      tpch9g.partsupp ps ON l.l_partkey = ps.ps_partkey JOIN      tpch9g.supplier s ON ps.ps_suppkey = s.s_suppkey;

SELECT      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus,      SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,      SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS sum_disc_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS sum_charge,      AVG(l_quantity) AS avg_qty,      AVG(l_extendedprice) AS avg_price,      AVG(l_discount) AS avg_disc,      COUNT(*) AS count_order FROM      tpch5g.lineitem GROUP BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus ORDER BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus;
SELECT SUM(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))))  FROM tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT      o.o_orderkey,      l.l_partkey,      l.l_quantity,      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))))) AS exp_val,      LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity)))))) AS log_val,      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity)))))) AS sin_val,      COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(l.l_quantity)))))) AS cos_val FROM      tpch9g.orders o  JOIN      tpch9g.lineitem l  ON      o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE      l.l_quantity > 50;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_quantity, l_extendedprice FROM tpch9g.lineitem WHERE l_discount > 0.05 ORDER BY l_extendedprice DESC, l_quantity ASC;

SELECT      n.n_name,      r.r_name,      AVG(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))) AS avg_exp_quantity FROM      tpch1g.lineitem l JOIN      tpch1g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN      tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN      tpch1g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey JOIN      tpch1g.region r ON n.n_regionkey = r.r_regionkey WHERE      l.l_quantity > 5 GROUP BY      n.n_name, r.r_name;

SELECT l_returnflag, l_linestatus, SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity, SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_price, AVG(l_discount) AS avg_discount FROM tpch5g.lineitem GROUP BY l_returnflag, l_linestatus ORDER BY total_quantity DESC;

SELECT     n.n_name,     SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM     tpch500m.lineitem l JOIN     tpch500m.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN     tpch500m.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN     tpch500m.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE     l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY     n.n_name ORDER BY     revenue DESC;

SELECT EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))))),         LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity)))))),         SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity))))))  FROM tpch9g.lineitem l  WHERE l.l_quantity > 50;
SELECT EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))),         LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))),         SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity))))))  FROM tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus,      SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,      SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS sum_disc_price,      SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS sum_charge,      AVG(l_quantity) AS avg_qty,      AVG(l_extendedprice) AS avg_price,      AVG(l_discount) AS avg_disc,      COUNT(*) AS count_order  FROM      tpch500m.lineitem  GROUP BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus  ORDER BY      l_returnflag,      l_linestatus;

SELECT      o.o_orderkey,      o.o_orderdate,      l.l_partkey,      l.l_quantity FROM      tpch500m.orders o JOIN      tpch500m.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey WHERE      o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1995-01-01' AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1996-01-01' ORDER BY      o.o_orderdate DESC, l.l_quantity DESC;

SELECT o.o_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_quantity,         EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity))) AS exp_quantity,         LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity + 1))) AS log_quantity,         SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity))) AS sin_quantity,         COS(COS(COS(l.l_quantity))) AS cos_quantity FROM tpch1g.orders o JOIN tpch1g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey ORDER BY o.o_orderkey, l.l_partkey, l.l_quantity;

SELECT      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l.l_quantity)))))),      LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l.l_quantity)))))),      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l.l_quantity))))))  FROM      tpch5g.lineitem l JOIN      tpch5g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN      tpch5g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey;

SELECT      c.c_name,      o.o_orderdate,      l.l_extendedprice FROM      tpch5g.customer c JOIN      tpch5g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN      tpch5g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey;

SELECT l_orderkey, l_partkey, l_quantity,      EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity)))))) AS exp_val,      LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(LOG(l_quantity)))))) AS log_val,      SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) AS sin_val,      COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(COS(l_quantity)))))) AS cos_val FROM tpch1g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;
SELECT l_quantity  FROM tpch9g.lineitem  ORDER BY SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity))))));

SELECT     n.n_name,     SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_sales FROM     tpch1g.orders o JOIN     tpch1g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN     tpch1g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE     o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY     n.n_name ORDER BY     total_sales DESC;
SELECT l_quantity, SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) FROM tpch500m.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;

SELECT      n.n_name,      SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM      tpch500m.lineitem l JOIN      tpch500m.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN      tpch500m.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN      tpch500m.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey GROUP BY      n.n_name ORDER BY      revenue DESC;
SELECT SUM(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(EXP(l_quantity))))))) FROM tpch500m.lineitem;
SELECT SIN(l_quantity), COS(l_quantity), TAN(l_quantity), EXP(l_quantity), LOG(l_quantity + 1) FROM tpch500m.lineitem;

SELECT l_returnflag, l_linestatus,         SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,         SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,         SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS sum_disc_price,         SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS sum_charge,         AVG(l_quantity) AS avg_qty,         AVG(l_extendedprice) AS avg_price,         AVG(l_discount) AS avg_disc,         COUNT(*) AS count_order FROM lineitem GROUP BY l_returnflag, l_linestatus ORDER BY l_returnflag, l_linestatus;

SELECT     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus,     SUM(l_quantity) AS total_quantity,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS total_extendedprice,     AVG(l_discount) AS avg_discount FROM     tpch500m.lineitem WHERE     l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus ORDER BY     total_quantity DESC,     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus;

SELECT     n.n_name,     SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM     tpch9g.lineitem l JOIN     tpch9g.orders o ON l.l_orderkey = o.o_orderkey JOIN     tpch9g.customer c ON o.o_custkey = c.c_custkey JOIN     tpch9g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE     l.l_shipdate BETWEEN DATE '1995-01-01' AND DATE '1996-12-31' GROUP BY     n.n_name ORDER BY     revenue DESC;

SELECT     c.c_name,     n.n_name,     SUM(o.o_totalprice) AS total_spent FROM     customer c JOIN     orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN     nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE     o.o_orderdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'     AND o.o_orderdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY     c.c_name,     n.n_name ORDER BY     total_spent DESC,     c.c_name;

SELECT      n.n_name,      SUM(l.l_extendedprice * (1 - l.l_discount)) AS revenue FROM      tpch9g.customer c JOIN      tpch9g.orders o ON c.c_custkey = o.o_custkey JOIN      tpch9g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey JOIN      tpch9g.nation n ON c.c_nationkey = n.n_nationkey WHERE      l.l_shipdate >= DATE '1995-01-01'      AND l.l_shipdate < DATE '1996-01-01' GROUP BY      n.n_name ORDER BY      revenue DESC;
SELECT l_quantity FROM tpch9g.lineitem ORDER BY l_quantity;

SELECT      o.o_orderkey,      l.l_partkey,      l.l_quantity,      p.p_name,      s.s_name  FROM      tpch9g.orders o  JOIN      tpch9g.lineitem l ON o.o_orderkey = l.l_orderkey  JOIN      tpch9g.part p ON l.l_partkey = p.p_partkey  JOIN      tpch9g.supplier s ON l.l_suppkey = s.s_suppkey  ORDER BY      o.o_orderkey,      l.l_partkey,      p.p_name,      s.s_name;
SELECT l_orderkey, l_quantity, SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(SIN(l_quantity)))))) AS complex_calc FROM tpch5g.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50 ORDER BY complex_calc;

SELECT     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus,     SUM(l_quantity) AS sum_qty,     SUM(l_extendedprice) AS sum_base_price,     SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount)) AS sum_disc_price,     SUM(l_extendedprice * (1 - l_discount) * (1 + l_tax)) AS sum_charge,     AVG(l_quantity) AS avg_qty,     AVG(l_extendedprice) AS avg_price,     AVG(l_discount) AS avg_disc,     COUNT(*) AS count_order FROM     tpch1g.lineitem WHERE     l_shipdate <= DATE '1998-12-01' - INTERVAL '90' DAY GROUP BY     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus ORDER BY     l_returnflag,     l_linestatus;
SELECT SUM(POWER(l_quantity, 2)) FROM tpch500m.lineitem WHERE l_quantity > 50;
